v0.1 is on Chrome Web Store: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/kldijfbphampndgemooecbdgfdnmhhjl


To load an open Chrome Plugin:
http://code.google.com/chrome/extensions/getstarted.html#load

How to use:
After extension is loaded, highlight and right click on any chunk of text to search on Linkedin.

Currently, only the Company Insider Plugin is being used. Possible future additions may include the Member Profile Plugin and other Linkedin Connect Plugins located at http://developer.linkedin.com/community/plugins
